    "body": "I'm supportive of adding overloads with a `count` arg for both the `expectEmit` and `expectCall` cheats, since that accomplishes both this issue and #4513 with the same UX/set of cheats. I saw in the support telegram that you'd be interested in working on this, should I assign to you?\r\n\r\nAlso if anyone has objections to that syntax and has a reason to prefer e.g. `expectNoEmit` please share ðŸ™‚",
